# ─── ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# On Vercel: go to Project → Settings → Environment Variables and add these

# Your Google Gemini API key — FREE at https://aistudio.google.com
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# ─── HOW TO GET YOUR FREE GEMINI API KEY (2 minutes) ─────────────────────────
# 1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Get API Key" → "Create API key"
# 4. Copy the key and paste it above
# FREE limits: 1,500 requests/day, 1 million tokens/day — more than enough!

# ─── VERCEL DEPLOYMENT STEPS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Push this project to GitHub
# 2. Go to https://vercel.com → "Add New Project" → Import from GitHub
# 3. Before deploying: go to Project Settings → Environment Variables
#    Add: GEMINI_API_KEY = your-key-here
# 4. Deploy → your app is live at https://your-project.vercel.app
